Change all "6.8.1" and "6\.8\.1" in this document to the current version
identifier:

    :%s/6\.8\.1/x.x.x/g
    :%s/6\\\.6\\\.5/x\\.x\\.x/g

Ensure that the configure(1) script is up-to-date:

    autoconf

Ensure that the package builds on all systems:

    ./remoteBuild all

Edit certain files:

    vi VERSION
    vi CHANGE_LOG
    vi RELEASE_NOTES
    vi ANNOUNCEMENT

Edit the release notes for the online documentation:

    vi ../doc/release-notes.html

Update the version information in the documentation:

    vi ../doc/macros.make
    vipat '6\.8' ../doc/*.html ../doc/basics/*.html

Copy the change-log to the documentation directory:

    cp CHANGE_LOG ../doc

Update the supported-platforms information:

    vi ../doc/basics/platform.html remoteBuild

Commit changes to the documentation:

    (cd ../doc && cvs commit)

Create the (hidden) online documentation:

    (cd ../doc && make)

Commit all changes:

    sce commit

Create the FTP distribution:

    make ftp

Install the package on Conan:

    ssh ldm@conan
    exec bash --login
    gunzip -c /web/ftp/pub/ldm/ldm-6.8.1.tar.gz | pax -r &&
	cd ldm-6.8.1/src
    vi '+/listen(sock/' server/ldmd.c		# change "32" to "512"
    ./configure CFLAGS=-g CPPFLAGS=-UNDEBUG \
	    >&configure.log && 
	make >&make.log &&
	make install >&install.log && 
	../bin/pqcheck -vl- &&
	echo OK

    /usr/ccs/bin/make install_setuids	# as "root"

    cd &&
	ldmadmin stop &&
	rm runtime &&
	ln -s ldm-6.8.1 runtime &&
	ldmadmin start &&
	ldmadmin watch
    exit

Online the hidden documentation on Conan:

    ssh conan
    cd /content/software/ldm
    vi '+/6\.6\.4/' index.html
    rm ldm-current && ln -s ldm-6.8.1 ldm-current
    cd /content/downloads/ldm
    vi '+/6\.6\.4/' toc.xml
    exit

Post ANNOUNCEMENT to "ldm-users@unidata.ucar.edu" with RELEASE_NOTES attached.
